OL,3,CThousands of homes and businesses
OL,4,Cexperiencing water supply problems
OL,6,FAround 5,600 properties in Tunbridge
OL,7,FWells are experiencing water supply
OL,8,Fissues, including low pressure,
OL,9,Fintermittent supply or no water.
OL,11,FIt's the latest in a spate of problems
OL,12,Ffor customers of South East Water.
OL,14,FIncident Manager, Robert Anthony-
OL,15,FScorse, said: "We're very sorry to our
OL,16,Fcustomers in the Tunbridge Wells area.
OL,18,F"This is due to a technical issue at
OL,19,Four water treatment works in the area,
OL,20,Fwhich has impacted levels in our local
OL,21,Fdrinking water storage tanks.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
