OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784477892
OL,3,CThousands of homes and businesses
OL,4,Cexperiencing water supply problems
OL,6,F"It has meant we have been unable to
OL,7,Fpump water to properties in the
OL,8,FTunbridge Wells area, particularly
OL,9,Fthose on higher ground.
OL,11,F"We're working hard to resolve the
OL,12,Fissue as soon as possible."
OL,14,FTankers are being used to increase
OL,15,Fdrinking water storage levels to help
OL,16,Fsupport the affected areas.
OL,18,FDeliveries of bottled water to
OL,19,Fcustomers on our Priority Services
OL,20,FRegister.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
